==English==

===Etymology===
From {{term|geometric}} and {{term|-ian}}, presumably by analogy with other words in {{term|-ician}}, such as {{term|mathematician}}.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[geometer]]; a [[mathematician]] specializing in the study of [[geometry]].

